                  "html": "<div style=\"max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 48px\"><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7c3aed;margin:0 0 28px 0;font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif\">— Disponible pour nouveaux projets</p><h1 style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(48px,6vw,88px);font-weight:800;line-height:0.95;margin:0 0 32px 0\"><span style=\"display:block;color:#fafafa\">Design &amp;</span><span style=\"display:block;-webkit-text-stroke:2px #fafafa;color:transparent\">Development.</span><span style=\"display:block;color:#fafafa\">Expérience.</span></h1><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:#71717a;max-width:480px;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 48px 0\">Je transforme vos idées en interfaces élégantes et performantes. Spécialisé en UX/UI design, développement front-end et identité de marque.</p><div style=\"display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap\"><a href=\"/projets\" style=\"background:#7c3aed;color:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:4px;font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block\">Voir mes projets →</a><a href=\"/contact\" style=\"background:transparent;color:#fafafa;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block\">Me contacter →</a></div><div style=\"margin-top:72px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);display:flex;gap:40px;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div><p style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:#7c3aed;line-height:1;margin:0 0 6px 0\">60+</p><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#71717a;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">PROJETS LIVRÉS</p></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:#7c3aed;line-height:1;margin:0 0 6px 0\">7 ans</p><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#71717a;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">D&#39;EXPÉRIENCE</p></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:#7c3aed;line-height:1;margin:0 0 6px 0\">100%</p><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#71717a;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">CLIENTS SATISFAITS</p></div></div></div>"
