                  "html": "<div style=\"max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 48px\"><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7c3aed;margin:0 0 16px 0\">— Services</p><h2 style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:800;color:#fafafa;margin:0 0 48px 0;line-height:1\">Ce que je propose</h2><div><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#71717a;font-weight:500;min-width:24px\">01</span><span style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa\">UX/UI Design</span></div><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;max-width:320px;text-align:right;margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Conception d&#39;interfaces intuitives centrées utilisateur. Research, wireframes, prototypes interactifs Figma.</p></div><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#71717a;font-weight:500;min-width:24px\">02</span><span style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa\">Développement Front-End</span></div><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;max-width:320px;text-align:right;margin:0;line-height:1.6\">React, Next.js, TypeScript. Code propre, performant, accessible. Du design au pixel perfect.</p></div><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#71717a;font-weight:500;min-width:24px\">03</span><span style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa\">Identité de Marque</span></div><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;max-width:320px;text-align:right;margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Logos, chartes graphiques, design systems complets. Une identité cohérente sur tous vos supports.</p></div><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#71717a;font-weight:500;min-width:24px\">04</span><span style=\"font-family:'Syne',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa\">Motion &amp; Animation</span></div><p style=\"font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;max-width:320px;text-align:right;margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Animations UI, transitions, micro-interactions. Les détails qui transforment une bonne interface.</p></div></div></div>"
